params.newMerkleRoot: The merkle root to assign to the new tier. Requirements:  - Caller must be an admin  - Tier must already be added to TellerNFT

params.account: The address to claim NFTs on behalf.
params.requests: An array requests data generated from the merkle tree. Requirements:  - Node in the merkle root must not be claimed already  - Proof of the node must match the merkle tree

addTier(bytes32).notice: Adds a new tier to be able to claim NFTs.

claim(address,(uint256,uint256,uint256,b.notice: Claims TellerNFTs for a given verifiable merkle proofs for each tier.

grantRole(bytes32,address).notice: Grants an address a new role. Requirements:  - Sender must be role admin.

initialize(address,address).notice: Initializes the Distributor contract with the TellerNFT

renounceRole(bytes32,address).notice: Grants an address a new role. Requirements:  - Sender must be role admin.

revokeRole(bytes32,address).notice: Removes a role from an address. Requirements:  - Sender must be role admin.
